## CONTEXT TRACKER (MANDATORY)

> Every session carries a **CTX score** (0έΑΥ280). When CTX έΚξ 180 the agent MUST warn. When CTX έΚξ 250 the agent MUST run `/end` autonomously.

| Zone | CTX | Action |
|------|-----|--------|
| Ώθθλ SAFE | 0έΑΥ100 | Continue normally |
| Ώθθκ WARN | 101έΑΥ180 | Wrap up subtask, plan /end |
| ΏθΦ┤ HIGH | 181έΑΥ250 | Start /end soon έΑΦ commit + handoff |
| έδΦ CRITICAL | 251έΑΥ280 | Execute /end NOW, then ask user to open new chat |

- **Agent:** `bun agent:run context_tracker --dry` έΑΦ run anytime, mandatory before long multi-step tasks
- **Auto-trigger rule:** If the agent detects CTX έΚξ 250 it MUST emit `/end` without waiting for user prompt
- **Score factors:** uncommitted files ├Ω 4, session commits ├Ω 2, changed code files ├Ω 1, handoff size (KB) ├Ω 0.5, agent runs ├Ω 8

